{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":7359,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"接收者只利用私钥就可以解密啦","timestamp":1592750588,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7380,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"并不是这么简单，事实上，RSA 的特殊设计（公钥、私钥地位对等）使得洞主可以使用私钥进行加密并发出，那么所有人也可以利用公钥取得这段信息","timestamp":1592750678,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7385,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"相当于同时也可以实现广播功能，并且在这样的匿名环境下，证明了这条广播的确由本人发出","timestamp":1592750702,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7396,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这个例子在 #767 和 #807 中得到了使用（如果还没被删的话）","timestamp":1592750746,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7405,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"嗯嗯，理解的基本没什么毛病，dz真棒！","timestamp":1592750776,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7415,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"事实上，在 #1159 中已经有了对此较为准确的介绍","timestamp":1592750822,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7419,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"如果想私密聊天得双方都有公钥和私钥。对于个人来说，加密信息用别人的公钥，数字签名用自己的私钥","timestamp":1592750845,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7420,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Bob说得对，不过那个是所谓的“数字签名”的功能，和dz说的功能是并列的关系","timestamp":1592750851,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7564,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re : 好 我已经理解了","timestamp":1592751529,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":7629,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":1473,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"看#1159就够了，dz说的很详细了","timestamp":1592751888,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":2,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":1473,"reply":10,"tag":null,"text":"我对RSA还是不太理解，稍微查了一下，我的理解是：\n\n接收者（例如一些洞主）自己生成一对公钥和私钥，将公钥发布\n其他想给接收者发送信息的人（例如Alice等），使用公钥将自己的信息进行加密发给接收者\n然后接收者利用公钥和私钥将加密后的内容解密，得到想发送的信息\n\n是这样吗？所以相当于一个单向的加密信息传输？","timestamp":1592750551,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782583,"url":"","vote":{}}}